        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The &quot;Loan For Commercial Pilot Training&quot; scheme was launched by the Tribal Development Department, Government of Gujarat. The scheme aims to support Scheduled Tribe (ST) students in pursuing professional pilot training by providing affordable loans. Under this scheme, tribal students can avail a loan at a concessional interest rate, enabling them to secure high-quality training and good employment opportunities.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "**Monetary Benefit**\n\n- Loan of up to ₹25,00,000 or the actual cost of training, whichever is lower.\n\n**Interest Rate**\n\n- 4% per annum.\n\n**Penalty Interest**\n\n- 2.5% per annum on delayed repayments.\n\n**Beneficiary Contribution**\n\n- No contribution is required from the applicant.\n\n**Repayment Terms**\n\n- Repayment begins 1 year after the loan disbursement date.\n- Repayment period is 144 monthly installments (12 years).\n- Includes 10 years for principal repayment and 2 years for interest repayment.\n- Early repayment is permitted.\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme aims to offer affordable loans of up to ₹25,00,000 at a 4% annual interest rate to tribal students who want to pursue pilot training.",
        "exclusions_md": "",
